platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 隱形潛入鄰屋，揭驚人秘密

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Few villains are as unsettling as this stealth game's creepy neighbor, who relentlessly pursues you through his increasingly bizarre house.
像這款潛行遊戲中的恐怖鄰居一樣的壞蛋實屬少有，在愈來愈奇怪的房子中，逃避他的無情追逐。
Few villains are as unsettling as this stealth game’s creepy neighbour, who relentlessly pursues you through his increasingly bizarre house.
Peu de méchants sont aussi troublants que le voisin de ce jeu de furtivité. Il vous poursuit sans relâche dans sa maison de plus en plus bizarre.
